description: A nice interview with Bob Brookmeyer from 1981 when he was in Minneapolis as a clinician working with the University of Minnesota jazz program.  The interview does not start at the beginning which did not survive on the tape and there is a Q & A section with musicians including Joe Pulice and Bob Parsons not included because the tape is severely warped.
